## 分步向导

```vue
<el-steps :active="currentStep" align-center>
  <el-step title="基础信息" />
  <el-step title="高级配置" />
</el-steps>
<StepBasic v-if="currentStep === 0" v-model="form.basic" />
<StepAdvanced v-if="currentStep === 1" v-model="form.advanced" />
<div class="form-footer">
  <el-button v-if="currentStep > 0" @click="handlePrev">上一步</el-button>
  <el-button v-if="currentStep < lastStep" type="primary" @click="handleNext">下一步</el-button>
  <el-button v-else type="primary" :loading="submitting" @click="handleSubmit">提交</el-button>
</div>
```

- 每步独立子组件 + 本步校验
- `useWizard.ts` 管理 `currentStep`、聚合 `form`、最终提交

