## 文件上传

```vue
<el-form-item label="附件" prop="fileUrl">
  <el-upload
    :action="uploadAction"
    :headers="uploadHeaders"
    :show-file-list="true"
    :limit="1"
    :on-success="handleUploadSuccess"
    :on-remove="handleUploadRemove"
  >
    <el-button type="primary">点击上传</el-button>
  </el-upload>
</el-form-item>
```

- 上传地址、鉴权 header 从 `project-conventions.md`、项目配置或 `services.ts` 获取，**禁止硬编码 token**
- 成功回调写入 `form.fileUrl`，删除时清空
- 多图、自定义上传、Excel 批量导入见 [高级表单控件开发指南.mdc](./高级表单控件开发指南.mdc)

